WEBVTT

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:02.656
We drew up a vision

00:11:02.680 --> 00:11:07.456
with a beneficial and commercially
sustainable supply chain for fonio,

00:11:07.480 --> 00:11:10.336
and we connected ourselves
with organizations

00:11:10.360 --> 00:11:11.960
that can help us achieve it.

00:11:13.360 --> 00:11:16.265
Walking backwards from the market,
here is what it looks like.

00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:23.896
Imagine that fonio
is consumed all across the globe

00:11:23.920 --> 00:11:27.560
as other popular ancient grains.

00:11:29.320 --> 00:11:32.376
Fonio touted on the levels of cereals,